data.description: Charming 3-Bed, 2-Bath Home with Pool & Workshop!Welcome to 719 NE Perch Lane, Port Saint Lucie! This 3-bed, 2-bath gem features a converted garage for flexible living, well-lit Florida room, and hurricane windows in bedrooms and front door.Notable upgrades include a new water heater (2023), AC system (2017), and a sleek metal roof (2017) that enhances durability and modern style.Step outside to a private oasis with a large pool, screened patio, and a substantial workshop shed with power in the expansive yard.Centrally located in a desirable neighborhood, this home is close to schools, shopping, and parks, offering convenience and comfort. Don't miss out--schedule a showing today and experience the charm of 719 NE Perch Lane!
